column2: "Darn it, I wonder where Huey could be."
"Supposedly, he's been dispatched to this area, but I haven't seen him at all..."
"\"It's okay as long as I'm here\"?. I'm old, don't put that kind of responsibility on me."
"The Labrys is still being repaired, and I haven't completely recovered from using it either."
"Right now, the one we can depend on most here is you, so have confidence and take the lead."
"But there's something around here that just gives me a bad feeling."
"Please don't try and scare us like that."
"It's not a scare tactic. Judging from the amount of Darker attacks in this area, there's definitely something they're after."
